    "RAG + Reranker retains the single-query retrieval approach but adds a reranking step.",
    "To support more diverse initial candidates, we retrieve the top-2k passages for the original query (2 × k candidates), which are then scored by a reranker.",
    "The top-k passages according to this score are selected as final input.",
    "RAG + QD + Reranker combines both components.",
    "It first decomposes the query into sub-queries, retrieves documents for each, merges the results, and applies reranking to select the final top-k passages."
